import { Modal, Stack, Form, Button } from "react-bootstrap";

function ModalAdd({ isModalAdd, setIsModalAdd }) {
  return (
    <Modal show={isModalAdd} onHide={() => setIsModalAdd(false)}>
      <Modal.Header closeButton>
        <Modal.Title>Agregar orden</Modal.Title>
      </Modal.Header>
      <Modal.Body>
        <Form>
          <Stack>
            <Form.Control
              controlId="idCompra"
              type="text"
              placeholder="ID Compra"
              className="mb-1"
            />
            <Form.Control
              controlId="cliente"
              type="text"
              placeholder="Cliente"
              className="mb-1"
            />
            <Form.Control
              controlId="fechaCompra"
              type="text"
              placeholder="Fecha de compra"
              className="mb-1"
            />
            <Form.Control
              controlId="fechaEntrega"
              type="text"
              placeholder="Fecha de entrega"
              className="mb-1"
            />
            <Form.Control
              controlId="courier"
              type="text"
              placeholder="Courier"
              className="mb-1"
            />
            <Form.Control
              controlId="tracking"
              type="text"
              placeholder="Tracking"
              className="mb-1"
            />
            <Form.Control
              controlId="costo"
              type="text"
              placeholder="Costo de compra"
              className="mb-1"
            />
            <Form.Control
              controlId="detalle"
              type="text"
              placeholder="Detalle"
              className="mb-1"
            />
            <Form.Control
              controlId="observacion"
              type="text"
              placeholder="Observacion"
              className="mb-1"
            />
            <Form.Control
              controlId="estado"
              type="text"
              placeholder="Estado"
              className="mb-1"
            />
          </Stack>
        </Form>
      </Modal.Body>
      <Modal.Footer>
        <Button variant="secondary" onClick={() => setIsModalAdd(false)}>
          Cancelar
        </Button>
        <Button variant="primary">Agregar</Button>
      </Modal.Footer>
    </Modal>
  );
}

export default ModalAdd;
